imdb.plot outline: Series follows a real-life, naturally-entertaining family, born and raised in the South, as they embark on a 'fish out of water' experience by visiting a fancy beach rental in the Hamptons for the summer, indulging in the high-end lifestyle of the Upper East Coast and bringing their southern flare to any situation.
